Hi Volks!

Mike's Bus wrote:
> So my question: can a '78 with a T4 2.0 Liter motor pull '70s Bug???

Sure.  Volkswagen rated the Type 4 powered Bus to be able
to tow 1,800 kg in Germany.  But don't go fast while towing --
you'll quickly overstress the engine IMHO.  The legal top 
speed with a trailer is 80 km/h (50 mph) in Germany.

Airhowlingly yours,
